.TH BEAVER-HELP 1 "February 2026" "Beaver" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
beaver-help \- Show Beaver help topics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B beaver-help
.RI [ topic ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B beaver-help
is a small wrapper that executes
.BR "beaver help" .
Use it to display the same topic-specific help available via
.BR beaver (1).
.SH TOPICS
.TP
.B ai
Help for the Beaver AI client.
.TP
.B internet
Help for text-based web browsing.
.TP
.B mail
Help for mail sync and clients.
.TP
.B social
Help for social client usage.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR beaver (1)
